ADDITIONAL NOTICE

This software implements cryptographic functions. The author is an
experienced information security professional but not a professional
cryptographer. This software was developed with AI-assisted tools and
has not been independently audited.

Use at your own risk. See README.md and THREAT_MODEL.md for a full
description of limitations and security properties.

The GPL license ensures that any distribution of this software,
modified or unmodified, must remain open source. This is intentional.
A closed-source fork of a security tool cannot be audited. Forks must
remain open.
